<div><head>Vers 5</head><!--2 Tim 3, 5-->
    
    <p xml:id=""><!-- interlinearis-->
        <p><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/IItim3_5" synch="1-2">habentes speciem</quote>
            <p>et ideo periculosi</p>
        </p>
        <p><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/IItim3_5" synch="3-4">qui¬
            <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>dem pietatis</quote>
            <p><lb ed="#S"/>religionis</p>
        </p>
        <p><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/IItim3_5" synch="5-5">virtutem</quote>
            <p>vel veritatem, id est caritatem</p>
        </p>
        <p><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/IItim3_5" synch="6-8">autem eius 
            <lb ed="#S"/>abnegantes</quote>
            <p><lb ed="#S"/>factis</p>
            <p><!-- marginalis--><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/IItim3_5" synch="1-4">HABENTES  SPE¬
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>CIEM  PIETATIS.</quote> Quia eadem 
                <lb ed="#S"/>sacramenta cum piis. 
                <lb ed="#S"/>Virtutem autem 
                <lb ed="#S"/>eius. Virtus chari¬
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>tas de corde puro, con¬
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>scientia bona et fide non 
                <lb ed="#S"/>ficta, hec est virtus quam 
                <lb ed="#S"/>nihil vincit. Nullus ignis 
                <lb ed="#S"/>nulli fluctus seculi, nulla 
                <lb ed="#S"/>flumina temptationis eam 
                <lb ed="#S"/>extinguunt. De hac dicitur 
                <lb ed="#S"/>Fortis est ut mors di
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>lectio. Sicut enim mors 
                <lb ed="#S"/>quando venit, resisti ei non potest. 
                <lb ed="#S"/>Sic contra violentiam 
                <lb ed="#S"/>charitatis nihil potest mun
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>dus. Econtraria data 
                <lb ed="#S"/>est similitudo. Quando enim 
                <lb ed="#S"/>mors ad auferendum vio
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>lentissima est, sic chari¬
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>tas ad salvandum vio
                <lb ed="#S" break="no"/>lenta est. Vel secundum aliam 
                <lb ed="#S"/>litteram : Veritatem autem 
                <lb ed="#S"/>eius, id est res pietatis. Abnegantes idem 
                <lb ed="#S"/>sensus.</p>
        </p>
        <p><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/IItim3_5" synch="9-10">et hos</quote>
            <p><!-- interlinearis--><lb ed="#S"/>tales</p>
        </p>
        <p><quote source="http://scta.info/resource/IItim3_5" synch="11-11">devita</quote>
            <p>ecce quare incepit de novissimis tem
                <lb ed="#S"/>poribus
            </p>
        </p>
    </p>
